metadata.name: Aferian PLC
metadata.description: Aferian Plc, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a B2B video streaming solutions company worldwide. It engages in the delivery of video experiences over IP using its end-to-end solution. The company develops and sells streaming devices and solutions, including licensing and support services; online video solutions; and set-top box devices, and associated operating and device management software. It is also involved in the development and sale of an end-to-end streaming platform and associated services to content owners, broadcasters, and Pay TV operators. The company was formerly known as Amino Technologies plc and changed its name to Aferian Plc in June 2021. Aferian Plc was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Cambridge, the United Kingdom.
